  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/862130/extras/0d5e34d356b2140b688076b284979b49.poster.avif?t=1757692099\" width=576 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/862130/extras/0d5e34d356b2140b688076b284979b49.webm?t=1757692099\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/862130/extras/0d5e34d356b2140b688076b284979b49.mp4?t=1757692099\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Rainy Day Racer is a 3D time-attack motor racing game set in a Scottish city where it rains all the time, all the time, just absolutely hammers it down every effing day. Featuring:<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Arcadey, forgiving handling physics, with no collision damage and gently railroaded drifting<br></li><li>Leaderboards and downloadable ghosts to chase</li><li>3 vehicles, including a quality transit van<br></li><li>3 courses (one bit is shared between two courses, so maybe more like 2.8 courses)<br></li><li>1 beautiful woman model who'll twirl and hold up a sign with your name on it if you set a good record</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/862130/extras/0d5e34d356b2140b688076b284979b49.poster.avif?t=1757692099\" width=576 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/862130/extras/0d5e34d356b2140b688076b284979b49.webm?t=1757692099\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/862130/extras/0d5e34d356b2140b688076b284979b49.mp4?t=1757692099\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Rainy Day Racer is a 3D time-attack motor racing game set in a Scottish city where it rains all the time, all the time, just absolutely hammers it down every effing day. Featuring:<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Arcadey, forgiving handling physics, with no collision damage and gently railroaded drifting<br></li><li>Leaderboards and downloadable ghosts to chase</li><li>3 vehicles, including a quality transit van<br></li><li>3 courses (one bit is shared between two courses, so maybe more like 2.8 courses)<br></li><li>1 beautiful woman model who'll twirl and hold up a sign with your name on it if you set a good record</li></ul>",
